contributions.notes:
"Chris Liebing presents 10 Years CLR - 10 exclusive tracks in the mix"

Released with digipak packaging with 16 page-booklet

Total duration: 64:35 minutes

Back cover reads: "Play on repeat and you'll have an endless loop running, since the mix starts and ends with the same track."

Distributed by WAS - Word And Sound / Germany
(p)+(c) 2010 - CLR Create Learn Realize

Hello fellow fans of electronic music,

I am happy that the CLR label already turned 10 years and is still rollin'. I have been Creating, Learning and Realizing a lot of things during this period and YOU made this possible. You supported me over all these years by listening and dancing to the music, or just with your smile and good vibes.

Of course all of this would also not work without those amazing artists who trust me in releasing their music, and without all of the special people who help me running the label and my life as a DJ. Thank you all for that from the bottom of my heart.

My vision is and will be to release Techno that works during peak moments and also "not so" peak moments on the dancefloor, in order to distract you from all the mind-made troubles of "life" and pull you into the here and now. I hope you will continue making this possible by just staying open-minded and interested in whatever comes out of CLR in the next 10 years.

Let's keep spreading love, peace and happiness!

Thanks for all,

Chris
